# Manage Content View Filters

Use this for `satellite_content_view_filters`.

## Steps
1. Define filter rules in `satellite_content_view_filters`.
2. Apply with `redhat.satellite.content_view_filter`.
3. Keep content view and repository references by name.
4. Use include/exclude settings explicitly in each filter item.

## Checklist
- Uses FQCN `redhat.satellite.content_view_filter`.
- Optional parameters use `default(omit)`.
- Works with the content view workflow.
